* This API is not generally intended for third party application developers. * Use the AndroidX * Media2 session * Library for consistent behavior across all devices. *

* Contains the result of {@link Session2Command}.

variables.name: RESULT_INFO_SKIPPED
variables.comment:
* Result code representing that the command is skipped or canceled. For an example, a seek
         * command can be skipped if it is followed by another seek command.

variables.name: RESULT_SUCCESS
variables.comment: * Result code representing that the command is successfully completed.

variables.name: RESULT_ERROR_UNKNOWN_ERROR
variables.comment: * Result code represents that call is ended with an unknown error.
